With abortion,
we've made killing acceptable

26:02.040 --> 26:03.640
  when there are other options -

26:03.640 --> 26:06.800
carrying the baby to term,
putting the baby up for adoption.

26:06.800 --> 26:08.160
Just like that.

26:08.160 --> 26:11.000
What about children who'd
be deformed or handicapped?

